parameters: Welcome to the department of "Giga Obliteration, Nullification And Destruction" or GONAD for short
You can call me ALICE, I am in charge of your registration and training before we can start pointing you at Giga.
Good.  Lets get started on training
A GIGA is a giant inteligent great adversary. In recent years they have started popping up all over the place.  We at GONAD have been charged by the government to deal with the threat as it arises.
I am ALICE, short for Artifical Liason Inteligence for Communication and Exexution.
I was made in order to act as a secretary for the entire GIGA operation.  I handle all elements of the base and am in constant communication with all member of the team.
This is the training area we used to train new recruits in the differnt forms of combat we generally engage in.
What a damn know it all.  Fine, get out of here.
Well, tomorrow you meet your team so you better get to bed.  Good luck
That went well.  Now there is a lot more to repelling Giga's than just hitting them,  they won't just let that happen.
Now for the final bit of training.  Sometimes there are more than one Giga in a city at the same time,  Usually they arent on the same side.
Now let's try you against a "real" Giga, this one will be on par to a weak GIGA that you might encounter out in the wild.  Go nuts.
Yeah, that's the thing, GIGA's are way stronger than you humans.
Well, tomorrow you meet your team so you better get to bed.  Good luck
